      <data key="d0">Hidden Units</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Hidden Units refer to the neurons in a neural network layer that are not directly visible in input or output layers.&lt;SEP&gt;Hidden units refer to internal layers of artificial neural networks that enhance the model's ability to learn from data.</data>
