    <node id="Eigenvalues">
      <data key="d0">Eigenvalues</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Eigenvalues are scalars associated with transformations represented by matrices and are key to understanding their properties.&lt;SEP&gt;Eigenvalues are special scalar values associated with a matrix, representing the factor by which the corresponding eigenvector is stretched or shrunk during linear transformations.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-f81436ceefbaa6d5dc02610dd8127f9b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-443f6360d2d3fc61bef3f5a8c109e2f2</data>
