    <node id="Real Symmetric Matrix">
      <data key="d0">Real Symmetric Matrix</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">A real symmetric matrix is a square matrix that is equal to its transpose and can be decomposed into real-valued eigenvectors and eigenvalues.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-f81436ceefbaa6d5dc02610dd8127f9b</data>
