      <data key="d0">Singular Value Decomposition (SVD)</data>
      <data key="d1">method</data>
      <data key="d2">Singular Value Decomposition is a method for factoring a matrix into three matrices, revealing important properties even when eigendecomposition is not applicable.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-f81436ceefbaa6d5dc02610dd8127f9b</data>
