    <node id="1940s-1960s Wave">
      <data key="d0">1940s-1960s Wave</data>
      <data key="d1">event</data>
      <data key="d2">The 1940s-1960s wave of deep learning is the first historical period characterized by early theories and models in biological learning and cybernetics.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-7030ceb5e481db7469c5a663054ab0ff</data>
