    <node id="1980s-1990s Wave">
      <data key="d0">1980s-1990s Wave</data>
      <data key="d1">event</data>
      <data key="d2">The 1980s-1990s wave of deep learning represents a significant period where connectionist approaches gained research focus.</data>
