    <node id="Neuroscience Perspective">
      <data key="d0">Neuroscience Perspective</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">The neuroscience perspective on deep learning suggests that insights from brain function can inform the development of intelligent behavior in machine learning models.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-7030ceb5e481db7469c5a663054ab0ff</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1768911143</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Cybernetics">
      <data key="d0">Cybernetics</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Cybernetics is a field that laid the groundwork for the first wave of neural network research, focusing on the principles of control and communication in animals and machines.&lt;SEP&gt;Cybernetics refers to the study of communication and control in living organisms and machines, particularly prevalent during the 1940s to 1960s.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-7030ceb5e481db7469c5a663054ab0ff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5f255acea8c3a7b10af84028b23d7ead</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1768911143</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Connectionism">
      <data key="d0">Connectionism</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Connectionism is a theoretical framework underpinning the second wave of deep learning that emphasizes the interconnectedness of simple units (neurons).&lt;SEP&gt;Connectionism is a movement in neural network research that emphasizes how neural connections underpin cognitive processes and learning.&lt;SEP&gt;Connectionism is an approach within cognitive science that focuses on understanding how cognitive processes can be modeled using neural networks.&lt;SEP&gt;Connectionism is the theory that cognitive processes can be understood and modeled by neural networks, proposing that intelligence arises from interconnected neurons.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-7030ceb5e481db7469c5a663054ab0ff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-24b6e16206da653229333e2acff91797&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cd0905a2bbd4a2e98ea5834719f28254&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3e301584dbc493504e638dde9613d0a9</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
