      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Probability and Information Theory deals with the mathematical study of randomness and the representation of information.&lt;SEP&gt;Probability and Information Theory is another mathematical tool discussed in Part I, crucial for machine learning.</data>
