      <data key="d1">method</data>
      <data key="d2">Gradient-Based Optimization is a method that uses the gradient of an objective function to find local minima or maxima.&lt;SEP&gt;Gradient-Based Optimization is a technique used to minimize functions in machine learning and other optimization problems.</data>
