    </node>
    <node id="ADALINE">
      <data key="d0">ADALINE</data>
      <data key="d1">method</data>
      <data key="d2">ADALINE is a machine learning model developed around the same time as the Perceptron, focused on predicting real numbers based on input data and learning from that data.</data>
