    <node id="Feedforward Deep Network">
      <data key="d0">Feedforward Deep Network</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">The feedforward deep network, or multilayer perceptron, is a type of deep learning model that maps input values to output values through a series of layers.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-ec8cde6747414a42b9f90501d7dd0d2a</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1768911165</data>
