    <node id="Computational Graphs">
      <data key="d0">Computational Graphs</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Computational graphs are a way to represent mathematical expressions as directed graphs, where nodes represent operations and edges represent the flow of data.</data>
