    <node id="Urinary Tract Infections">
      <data key="d0">Urinary Tract Infections</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Urinary tract infections are common complications for individuals with poorly controlled diabetes, often requiring careful monitoring and treatment.&lt;SEP&gt;Urinary tract infections are common among diabetics, especially following bladder instrumentation.&lt;SEP&gt;Urinary tract infections are infections that can complicate kidney disease and require vigilant treatment.</data>
