      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Acute complications refer to immediate and severe health issues that can arise from uncontrolled blood sugar levels in diabetes.&lt;SEP&gt;Acute complications of diabetes mellitus refer to sudden health issues that can arise due to poor management of the disease, such as hypoglycaemia and ketoacidosis.</data>
