      <data key="d0">Metabolic Syndrome</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Metabolic syndrome includes a clustering of conditions that increase the risk of heart disease and diabetes, often associated with IGT.&lt;SEP&gt;Metabolic syndrome is a clustering of conditions that increase the risk of heart disease and diabetes, often associated with abnormal glucose tolerance.&lt;SEP&gt;Metabolic syndrome is a cluster of conditions that increase the risk of heart disease, stroke, and diabetes, often diagnosed based on specific clinical criteria.</data>
