    <node id="Miglitol">
      <data key="d0">Miglitol</data>
      <data key="d1">method</data>
      <data key="d2">Miglitol is another α-glucosidase inhibitor that also delays carbohydrate absorption and is used in diabetes treatment.&lt;SEP&gt;Miglitol is another α-glucosidase inhibitor with a similar dosage and effect as acarbose.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-eb0252816f7fbee4c50f79ef3ee56063&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-453e4228f98ddea76e07ce405d13fd32</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
