      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Glycaemic control refers to the management of blood glucose levels, crucial in preventing and managing diabetic retinopathy and other complications.&lt;SEP&gt;Glycaemic control refers to the management of blood sugar levels in individuals, which can help reduce the progression of diabetic complications.</data>
