      <data key="d2">Diabetes care involves managing diabetes through prevention, screening, and treatment to minimize health complications.&lt;SEP&gt;Diabetes Care is a journal that publishes research related to diabetes, including prevalence studies and clinical practice recommendations.&lt;SEP&gt;Diabetes Care is a journal that publishes research and guidelines related to the management and treatment of diabetes.</data>
