      <data key="d0">Angiotensin-Converting Enzyme Inhibitors</data>
      <data key="d1">method</data>
      <data key="d2">Angiotensin-Converting Enzyme Inhibitors are a class of medications that help manage hypertension and reduce kidney pressure.</data>
