      <data key="d0">Dietary Protein Restriction</data>
      <data key="d1">method</data>
      <data key="d2">Dietary protein restriction is a dietary approach aimed at reducing renal perfusion and slowing kidney damage in diabetic patients.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-fd4cfbed43aa26af0eef694fecac2177</data>
