      <data key="d0">Economic Barriers</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Economic barriers refer to financial challenges that prevent patients from seeking necessary diabetes care.&lt;SEP&gt;Economic barriers are obstacles preventing patients from obtaining appropriate care and treatments.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-fd4cfbed43aa26af0eef694fecac2177&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-55d2691a8c714949752d249721fec5e7</data>
