      <data key="d0">Oral Glucose Tolerance Test</data>
      <data key="d1">method</data>
      <data key="d2">The Oral Glucose Tolerance Test (OGTT) is a definitive confirmatory diagnostic test for diabetes mellitus that measures glucose levels after an oral glucose load.</data>
