    <node id="Triglycerides">
      <data key="d0">Triglycerides</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Triglycerides are a type of fat in the blood, which can have atherogenic properties, especially when elevated.&lt;SEP&gt;Triglycerides are a type of fat in the blood that can increase the risk of pancreatitis and cardiovascular conditions when elevated.&lt;SEP&gt;Triglycerides are a type of fat found in the blood that can increase the risk of heart disease when levels are elevated.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-a07cef05efd947a538701b4c41b162b1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8361af576f7e73b0bd2ea813976f60b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-21112bd6ed1fe7896dbf55a52bc45a2d</data>
