    <node id="Neuropathy">
      <data key="d0">Neuropathy</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Neuropathy is a general term used to describe disorders of the peripheral nerves, including diabetic neuropathy as a specific type.&lt;SEP&gt;Neuropathy refers to a condition that affects the nerves, leading to symptoms such as tingling and loss of sensation, particularly associated with diabetes.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-55d2691a8c714949752d249721fec5e7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0748670b42b0f4e0b2ed9c5ce62d54e7</data>
