    <node id="IGT">
      <data key="d0">IGT</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">IGT, or Impaired Glucose Tolerance, is identified as a risk category for future diabetes and related diseases; it often involves normal glycated hemoglobin levels.&lt;SEP&gt;IGT, or impaired glucose tolerance, is a prediabetic state that increases the risk of developing type 2 diabetes mellitus.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-42a410eaaaed4b7428f5e95a4c7c4580&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c4d75b2c01d2448f37de4deec12208fa</data>
