      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">IFG, or Impaired Fasting Glucose, is a metabolic condition characterized by specific fasting plasma glucose levels indicating a risk for diabetes.&lt;SEP&gt;IFG, or impaired fasting glucose, is another prediabetic condition characterized by higher than normal fasting blood sugar levels.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-42a410eaaaed4b7428f5e95a4c7c4580&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c4d75b2c01d2448f37de4deec12208fa</data>
