    <edge source="LDL Cholesterol" target="Statins">
      <data key="d7">2.0</data>
      <data key="d8">Statins are prescribed to reduce LDL cholesterol levels to manage cardiovascular risk.&lt;SEP&gt;Statins are used to reduce LDL cholesterol levels in patients who are intolerant to other cholesterol-lowering medications.</data>
